snippet.title: Johnny Depp career destroyed by lies and the willing media.
snippet.description:
Just a few short years ago Johnny Depp could only be mentioned in the same breath as actors like Leonardo DeCaprio and Brad Pitt. Now he has become a legend without work and without the backing of Hollywood. What he does have is the backing of Millions of his fans , who have stayed by his side and supported him and turned on the she devil herself Amber Heard. No one knows if Johnny Depp will come back from these lies but the one constant thing he has is the loyalty of his many many fans.
